{"lastModified":1775133344334,"uri":"c::10120242293::vessel::d5cca354-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nThis yacht features three luxurious double cabins, each with a private en-suite bathroom, offering unrivaled comfort for up to six guests. The master cabin, with a king-size bed, offers an oasis of tranquility, while the two guest cabins ensure ample space for relaxation. For the crew, two additional cabins provide comfort and privacy to maintain excellent service without interrupting guests' experience.\n\nThe fully equipped galley ensures a luxurious dining experience, with modern appliances including a Miele dishwasher, Siemens coffee machine, and ample refrigeration. Solar panels enhance energy efficiency, while the ice maker is perfect for chilled refreshments on warm day.\n\n\"Emerald Gemini\" is equipped for adventure, with a variety of water toys including paddleboards, a kneeboard, snorkeling gear, and a donut for exciting fun on the water. The basic fishing gear provides an opportunity for some peaceful angling during your voyage.\n\nExperience the height of comfort with electric toilets, a watermaker for freshwater independence, plush towels, and luxurious toiletries provided for every guest. A walk-in closet adds an extra touch of convenience and luxury.\n\nThe Meaning Behind \"Emerald Gemini\"\n\nThe name \"Emerald Gemini\" blends natural elegance with celestial symbolism.\n\nEmerald evokes the rich green hues of the gemstone and emerald eyes, symbolizing luxury, renewal, and tranquility, reflecting the calm beauty of the sea.\n\nGemini, the zodiac sign of the twins, represents duality, adaptability, and balance, perfectly capturing the yacht’s versatility—combining adventure with relaxation and power with elegance.\n\nEmerald Gemini\" reflects a luxurious and multi-faceted journey, where elegance meets innovation, and every moment aboard balances the thrill of discovery with the calm of the sea. It’s not just a name, but an invitation to experience life’s finest pleasures.","blueprint":{"name":"EMERALD GEMINI","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca354-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ec8428c0-fdca-11ef-96fb-a79c600940b3/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca354-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ec8e3ae0-fdca-11ef-8de3-1185cd49c674/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca354-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ec8c8d30-fdca-11ef-8de3-1185cd49c674/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca354-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ec84c500-fdca-11ef-96fb-a79c600940b3/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca354-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ec890ac0-fdca-11ef-aa0e-c3a23745a65e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca354-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ec8dc5b0-fdca-11ef-8de3-1185cd49c674/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca354-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ec905dc0-fdca-11ef-8de3-1185cd49c674/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca354-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ec8b54b0-fdca-11ef-8de3-1185cd49c674/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca354-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ec8672b0-fdca-11ef-91a2-55c32f2fec3f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca354-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ec886e80-fdca-11ef-96fb-a79c600940b3/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca354-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ec8428c0-fdca-11ef-aa0e-c3a23745a65e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca354-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ec851320-fdca-11ef-96fb-a79c600940b3/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca354-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ec8958e0-fdca-11ef-aa0e-c3a23745a65e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca354-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ec8f7360-fdca-11ef-8de3-1185cd49c674/{imageVariant}","/media